The paper also involves the use of approximation algorithms, which is a topic in theoretical computer science (cs.CC) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper involves the study of the diminishing returns property, which is a concept in game theory (cs.GT). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.DS and cs.DM, followed by cs.GT, cs.CC, and cs.LG.
